  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And between-- one time they really call me to the army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My sister, meanwhile, finished nursing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was working for the-- the military hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was a-- a specialist in [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] x-- not on x-ray.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, they used to bring the transports with thOSE butchered up-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when they-- I was getting there, and she had a bus, was a military man, a Jew, a Russian Jew with this wife.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she introduced me to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I told them to once about the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he said, you know, if you worked here, you would have [NON-ENGLISH], which is exemption from the army, because it's a military place.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But you have to be a member of the party.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I can't take you to statistics here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said, well, I'm not a member in the party.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well anyway, I got a job, and I was the only one that ever worked in this department because we were getting how many cripples they have and everything.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was working just with one older woman that she was is this apartment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So meanwhile I was safe from the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then-- then the hospital-- when the war started to get better for the Russians, the hospital had to go up front.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] No, that's not the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I get-- I get a letter when the water started to go good for the Russians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the town from where I came, Rovno, was liberated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I get a notice from the [NON-ENGLISH], which means from the army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I have a choice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Or I go in the army or I go back and work in the post, in the division from the telegraphs.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
